name: The Melancholy of the Girl who Found Refuge in the Night Garden
description:
"Hello, spirits of the garden. May I move in with you?
I can't find a home in my town anymore. The crisis is true.
The working soul in me is now forced to move away,
But I am still hoping to afford my own home someday." //

"Corruption, little seeker, has been turning everything into a game,
For many greedy launderers have set it all into flames.
Please find home in this vast garden, where you can let your heart go free,
Away from the dark forces, here, all you have to do is be." //
